text: New F&B enclave in the quiet science park area. Have a few interesting new F&B concepts that serves affordable and value for money meals.
Nothing spectacular. There are a cafeteria Chilli Api, Starbucks and a vegetarian. The place is mostly filled with office workers around the area.
Ate at Chili API. Food is decent but price is a little on the high side ..
Closed on weekends, wasted trip. And on another occasion the only open restaurant was having a private function.
A place that make heart warming at night
